Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,===============OP=================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,===============ED=================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.14,0:00:04.11,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,今はまだ明日がある
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.58,0:00:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, there is still a tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.49,0:00:07.93,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ルルーシュ·ランペルージには夢を見るべき明日がある
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.91,0:00:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,For Lelouch Lamperouge,\Nthere is still a tomorrow he can dream of.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.47,0:00:12.57,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そのよりどころこそ謎の少女C.C.から手に入れた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.95,0:00:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A dream based on the Geass\Nhe alone possesses...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.62,0:00:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,which was given to him\Nby the mysterious girl C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.59,0:00:14.20,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,彼だけのギアス
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.31,0:00:18.25,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いかなる相手にでも命令を下せる絶対遵守の力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.72,0:00:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The absolute power to\Ncompel anyone to obey him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.74,0:00:23.38,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fscx80}ギアスを使い　ルルーシュは神聖ブリタニア帝国の破壊を決意する
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.20,0:00:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Using his Geass, Lelouch is determined\Nto destroy the Holy Britannian Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.59,0:00:25.70,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,すべては母の敵を討ち
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.03,0:00:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All to avenge the death of his mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.78,0:00:29.66,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,妹ナナリーが幸せに過ごせる世界をつくるために
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.24,0:00:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and to create a world in which his\Nyounger sister Nunnally can live happily.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.36,0:00:33.81,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,植民地エリア11となった日本は
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.97,0:00:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,From Japan, now the colony called Area 11,\Na vow to the world begins to be realized.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.92,0:00:36.98,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,今　世界に向けた　誓いが始まる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.44,0:00:42.79,opj-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\fad(100,100)\an2}朝も夜も恋い焦がれて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.74,0:00:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Asa mo yoru mo koikogarete\NMorning and night, I long for you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.83,0:00:45.55,opj-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\fad(100,100)\an2}星になるよ 君守る
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.28,0:00:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,hoshi ni naru yo kimi mamoru\NI'll become a star and protect you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.63,0:00:48.95,opj-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\fad(100,100)\an2}戦いは行方知らず
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.05,0:00:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,tatakai wa yukue shirazu\NNo matter where the battle may take me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.97,0:00:54.00,opj-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\fad(100,100)\an2}明日と昨日の交差点で
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.98,0:00:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,ashita to kinou no kousaten de\NAt the intersection of tomorrow and yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.07,0:00:56.90,opj-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\fad(100,100)\an2}交わらない君と僕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.49,0:00:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,majiwaranai kimi to boku\NYou and I can't be together
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.96,0:01:00.11,opj-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\fad(100,100)\an2}今行くよ 僕は流れ星
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.36,0:01:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,ima iku yo boku wa nagareboshi\NI'm a shooting star, on my way right now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.63,0:01:11.38,opj-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\fad(100,100)\an2}世界が朽ち果てても 変わることの無いものがある
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.93,0:01:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,sekai ga kuchihatetemo\NEven if the world crumbles apart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.80,0:01:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,kawaru koto no nai mono ga aru\NThere are things which will never change
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.40,0:01:17.13,opj-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\fad(100,100)\an2}涙を堪えてでも 守るべきものが僕らにはある
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.67,0:01:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,namida wo koraete demo\NEven as we bear tears in our eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.17,0:01:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,mamorubeki mono ga bokura ni wa aru\NThere are things we must protect
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.15,0:01:17.91,opj-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\fad(100,100)\an2}（nononono）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.31,0:01:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,nanman'nen nan'okunen mae kara no\NA message that's been in my body
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.93,0:01:19.71,opj-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\fad(100,100)\an2}遅れまいと メッセージが絶えない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.45,0:01:18.85,opj-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\fad(100,100)\an2}（no）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.75,0:01:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,message ga tainai de\NFor thousands and millions of years,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.92,0:01:22.29,opj-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\fad(100,100)\an2}剥き出す 撃ち抜く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.18,0:01:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,uzukidasu... mayoi wa nai\NSprings out... I have no reservations
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.18,0:01:21.53,opj-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\fad(100,100)\an2}（迷いは無い）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.42,0:01:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,narihibiku... kantan da\NRoars out... It's easy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.83,0:01:22.78,opj-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\fad(100,100)\an2}（簡単だ）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.80,0:01:28.35,opj-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\fad(100,100)\an2}しゃがれた声で 傷だらけの手で 君守る
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.85,0:01:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,shagareta koe de... asu wo yobu\NIn a hoarse voice... Calling tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.45,0:01:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,kizudarake no te de... kimi mamoru\NWith my wounded hands... I protect you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.41,0:01:31.01,opj-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\fad(100,100)\an2}way got you could like
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.92,0:01:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I continue to fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.06,0:01:33.95,opj-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\fad(100,100)\an2}way got you could like
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.66,0:01:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I continue to fight!
