Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.59,0:02:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,afureru kimi no namida boku ga ima ubaisaru\NI'll take away your overflowing tears right now
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.94,0:02:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,COUNTERATTACK AT THE GALLOWS
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.47,0:02:22.30,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,うん？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.44,0:02:23.60,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,子供
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.95,0:02:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,A child?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.52,0:02:35.77,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,はい　殺した人の数は覚えていません
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.26,0:02:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, I can't remember\Nhow many people I've killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.14,0:02:43.99,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fscx80}歯を磨いたり　食事をしたことを数える人はいません　同じことです
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.80,0:02:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody counts the number of times\Nthey brush their teeth or eat meals.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.34,0:02:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Same with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.92,0:02:48.15,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,僕のギアスは暗殺に向いている
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.41,0:02:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,My Geass is suited to assassination.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.27,0:02:49.73,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そう言われました
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.91,0:02:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I was told. And so I killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.87,0:02:51.39,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,だから殺してきた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.79,0:02:53.62,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ほかにいる所もなかったし
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.32,0:02:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no other place where I could live.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.07,0:02:57.79,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,潜入工作　弟役ですか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.79,0:02:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,An infiltration operation?\NAnd I'd be playing a little brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.27,0:02:59.98,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,僕にやれるでしょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.95,0:03:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure I can pull this off?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.09,0:03:02.77,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,僕は親も家族も知りませんから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.82,0:03:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never known any parents or family, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.13,0:03:06.30,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いえ　それが命令なら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.69,0:03:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No. If that's your order...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.95,0:03:09.84,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,僕の兄は　ルルーシュ·ランペルージ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.46,0:03:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,then my big brother shall be Lelouch Lamperouge.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.35,0:03:16.33,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お前のギアスは時を止める能力か
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.07,0:03:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Geass is the power to stop time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.63,0:03:18.21,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,答える理由はありません
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.17,0:03:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no reason to answer you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.47,0:03:20.28,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,僕に与えられた指令は
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.08,0:03:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The orders given to me are as follows:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.38,0:03:23.32,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ルルーシュ·ランペルージの記憶が戻ったなら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.28,0:03:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If Lelouch Lamperouge's memories return...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.69,0:03:25.27,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ゼロが復活したなら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.21,0:03:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If Zero is reborn, then he is to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.42,0:03:26.47,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,抹殺する
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.07,0:03:28.01,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,16
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.55,0:03:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sixteen...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.36,0:03:30.30,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,17 18
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.92,0:03:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Seventeen... Eighteen... Nineteen...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.35,0:03:31.96,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なんです　その数字は
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.65,0:03:31.44,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,19
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.75,0:03:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that you're counting?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.34,0:03:33.88,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お前が現れたときから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.89,0:03:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you appeared, I've been\Ncounting the seconds to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.30,0:03:36.83,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,オレは心の中で時を数えていた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.08,0:03:39.79,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,だが　今はその数値がずれている
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.66,0:03:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But now the count is out of synch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.10,0:03:41.53,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なぜだと思う
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.86,0:03:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, why do you think that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.73,0:03:44.52,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ナナリーを捜すための駒になってもらう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}I'll make you my pawn to find Nunnally.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.12,0:03:54.25,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ロロ　お前が止めたのは時間ではない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.67,0:03:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Rolo, it isn't time that you're stopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.72,0:03:56.62,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,オレの体感時間だけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.21,0:03:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just my physical sensation of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.88,0:03:59.89,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それが分かったところで僕には勝てません
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.35,0:04:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you understand that, you can't beat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.82,0:04:04.44,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そう　誰も僕と同じ時間は　生きられない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.38,0:04:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}That's right... Nobody can live{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}in the same time with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.89,0:04:07.06,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ロロ　お前は正しい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.45,0:04:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Rolo, you're correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.71,0:04:11.31,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,すぐにオレを殺さないのは　分かっているからだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.42,0:04:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't kill me right away\Nbecause you know that, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.64,0:04:14.87,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,このままでは　2つとも手に入らないと
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.53,0:04:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,As things stand,\Nyou won't gain either of two things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.05,0:04:15.69,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,2つ？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.46,0:04:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Two things?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.78,0:04:19.17,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,1つは　このオレを餌に捜していたC.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.33,0:04:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,First, you won't get C.C., for which\NI've been the bait in your search.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.33,0:04:20.86,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,オレを見逃してくれたら
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.84,0:04:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If you let me go, I'll draw out C.C. for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.98,0:04:22.84,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,C.C.を　引きずり出してやろう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.63,0:04:25.55,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,売るのか　C.C.を
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.21,0:04:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd sell out C.C.?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.89,0:04:28.40,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,自分の命とは　比べられないからな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.48,0:04:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She isn't worth my own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.19,0:04:30.30,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,もう1つは
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.88,0:04:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And the other thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.56,0:04:31.76,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お前の命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.05,0:04:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.35,0:04:34.01,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ふっ　命なんて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.38,0:04:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I care about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.30,0:04:36.42,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ロロ　未来とはなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.82,0:04:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Rolo, what is the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.01,0:04:38.57,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,未来とは希望だ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.49,0:04:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The future is hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.89,0:04:41.43,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お前の任務の先に　希望はあるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.49,0:04:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any hope beyond your mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.58,0:04:43.74,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,C.C.を捕まえることで
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.43,0:04:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If you capture C.C., what sort\Nof future will it open for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.85,0:04:46.02,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お前にはどんな未来が開ける
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.20,0:04:49.10,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,今のままだ　何も変わらない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.86,0:04:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Things will just go on as they\Nare and nothing will change!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.44,0:04:50.86,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,これは任務だ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.87,0:04:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.09,0:04:53.47,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,オレを殺したら　任務は果たせない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill me and your mission will never be complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.68,0:04:55.59,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,C.C.を捕まえたいんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.24,0:04:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to capture C.C., don't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:04:59.46,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,明日　オレがC.C.を引きずり出してやろう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.07,0:05:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, I'll lure C.C. out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.80,0:05:02.38,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それでお前は新しい未来をつかめる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.38,0:05:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I do, a new future will be in your grasp!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.66,0:05:04.98,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,大丈夫　うそはつかないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.51,0:05:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I wouldn't lie to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.60,0:05:06.80,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お前にだけは…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.08,0:05:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Never to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.76,0:05:10.61,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,アオモリを思い出すわね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.39,0:05:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This reminds me of Aomori.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.65,0:05:11.96,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あれよりはましだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.05,0:05:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This is better than that was. At least\Neveryone here is wearing their clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:13.92,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,全員　服を着ているからな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.18,0:05:17.80,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,総領事にはゼロがギアスをかけたんでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero used his Geass on the consul\Ngeneral, right? So, why is he doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.09,0:05:19.34,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なのに　どうして
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.41,0:05:20.23,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,さぁな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.86,0:05:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows? Still, if they take this place\Naway from us, then we and Lelouch will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.50,0:05:24.06,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ただ　ここを取られると　私たちとルルーシュは…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.85,0:05:26.36,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,また　バラバラに
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.43,0:05:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...split up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.84,0:05:28.83,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,意外だな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.37,0:05:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How unexpected. You came alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.01,0:05:30.21,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,一人で来るとは
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.82,0:05:36.28,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,中華連邦の総領事は　合衆国日本を承認したはずだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.37,0:05:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought the Chinese Federation consul general\Nhad recognized the United States of Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.70,0:05:38.81,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,その方は　亡くなられる予定だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.15,0:05:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The plan is for him to be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.25,0:05:43.19,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それとも　ここで黒の騎士団がついえる道を選ぶか？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.82,0:05:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Or do the Black Knights choose\Nthe path of destruction right here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.26,0:05:44.81,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,待て　いきなりそんな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.75,0:05:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it! You can't just spring that on us...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.83,0:05:45.57,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,分かった
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.25,0:05:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. You can just arrange it so that\Nthe consul general is killed fighting us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.92,0:05:49.43,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,総領事は私たちと戦って死んだことにすればいい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.47,0:05:50.23,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.83,0:05:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,C.C.?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.59,0:05:53.36,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ゼロは思わぬ引き金を　引いたらしいな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.29,0:05:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems Zero has pulled a\Ntrigger he wasn't planning to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.67,0:05:57.00,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,高邁なる野望か　俗なる野心か
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.30,0:05:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Will this be noble ambition or base treachery?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.01,0:06:02.11,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,とりあえず　ロロが待つだけの時間は稼いだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.54,0:06:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Anyway, Rolo waiting for me{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}has bought me some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.37,0:06:04.33,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,C.C.が手に入るとなれば
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.01,0:06:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}If he gets C.C., he'll most likely{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}overlook my regaining my memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.43,0:06:06.78,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,オレの記憶のことは見過ごしてくれるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.97,0:06:09.99,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,だが　あいつの根源はなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.74,0:06:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Still, what is his motivation?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.21,0:06:13.36,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ブリタニアでの出世や忠誠とは違うようだが
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.11,0:06:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}It doesn't seem to be a desire for{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}promotion in Britannia or loyalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.57,0:06:14.84,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,とすると
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.58,0:06:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Or is there another line{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}of inquiry I should follow?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.09,0:06:17.31,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,もう一つのラインを探るべきか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.75,0:06:20.65,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,危険なカードだが　その分価値はある
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.22,0:06:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}That's a dangerous card,{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}but it has its merits.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.89,0:06:22.51,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,躊躇する余裕はない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.42,0:06:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}I don't have any time to hesitate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.77,0:06:25.66,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,明日には藤堂たちが処刑されてしまうのだから
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.39,0:06:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Because tomorrow, Tohdoh and the{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}others are going to be executed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.04,0:06:26.78,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どうする
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.56,0:06:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}What should I do?{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Rolo knows about my Geass now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.11,0:06:29.01,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,オレのギアスはロロにばれている
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.10,0:06:31.36,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なんとかロロを殺せたとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.00,0:06:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Even if I managed to kill him somehow, the O.S.I.{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}would know that I've regained my memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.46,0:06:34.14,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,オレの記憶が戻ったと機情に知られてしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.21,0:06:35.50,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうなれば　ナナリーが…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.67,0:06:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}And if that happens,{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}then Nunnally will be!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.07,0:06:41.48,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ナナリーを救い出すまでは　学生の振りを続けるしかないか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.81,0:06:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}I guess I'll have to keep playing student{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}until Nunnally has been rescued.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.97,0:06:42.82,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,幸い
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.55,0:06:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Fortunately, it looks like there's barely any{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}relationship between Guilford's men and the O.S.I.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.87,0:06:45.73,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ギルフォードたちと機情のつながりは薄いようだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.26,0:06:50.21,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fscx80}隠してあるナイトメアが発見されていないことからも　それは分かる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.88,0:06:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}The fact that they haven't found{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}the Knightmare I hid tells me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.32,0:06:52.17,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,だが　それだけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.22,0:06:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}But that's all I have in my favor.{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.37,0:06:53.51,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どうすればいい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.72,0:06:56.13,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,黒の騎士団を救い出し
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.62,0:06:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}How do I save the Black Knights and{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}take care of Rolo at the same time?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.15,0:06:58.81,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,同時にロロを排除する方法は
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.80,0:07:07.73,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,納得できません
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.94,0:07:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't accept that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.47,0:07:11.12,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ブルーノを殺したのはあのガキじゃないんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.10,0:07:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You're telling me you're going to\Noverlook that he killed Bruno?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.29,0:07:12.68,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,これで　5人目です
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.84,0:07:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the fifth one!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:15.51,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ビクトルなんて　ヤツのロケットに触っただけで
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.14,0:07:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,All Victor did was touch\Nthe kid's locket, and then!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.57,0:07:17.50,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,彼はふだんから問題があった
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.98,0:07:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Victor had his own personality problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.88,0:07:19.64,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,殺されるほどではないでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.48,0:07:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That didn't mean he had to be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.82,0:07:22.21,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ゼロを名乗る者が現れた以上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.45,0:07:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that we've got this guy claiming to be Zero,\Nwe have to get our priorities straight!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.33,0:07:24.56,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,我々はよりまとまらねば
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.79,0:07:28.25,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,仲間を殺すような死神とチームは組めません
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.35,0:07:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't be a teammate with a\Nguy who kills his own people!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.49,0:07:32.52,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,チーム？大事なのは任務でしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.99,0:07:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Team? The mission is what's important, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.75,0:07:33.96,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,仲間なんて
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.43,0:07:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares about teammates?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:39.25,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なあ　復活したゼロって　あのゼロかな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.07,0:07:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, is this new Zero the same as our Zero?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.30,0:07:40.07,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,さあな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.77,0:07:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.36,0:07:44.09,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どちらにしろ　また見捨てるつもりだろ　私たちを
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.07,0:07:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, we're probably\Ngoing to be abandoned again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.49,0:07:46.81,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,総領事館の爆発事故原因は
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.07,0:07:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What was the source of the\Nexplosions in the consulate?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.08,0:07:48.72,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いまだ　公式発表は
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.64,0:07:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,They still haven't issued a formal statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:52.13,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,刑の執行は認めるとの連絡があっただけです
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.78,0:07:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,All they've said is that they acknowledge\Nthe punishment to be carried out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.26,0:07:55.37,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,処刑など　ただの見せしめ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.88,0:07:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,An execution is just a warning to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.51,0:07:57.54,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,我ながら　品のない手段だ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.22,0:07:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This is so unrefined of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.78,0:07:59.54,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,現れるでしょうか　ゼロは
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.29,0:08:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You think Zero will show himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.78,0:08:01.68,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,出てこなければ　それでいい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.39,0:08:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if he doesn't, it'll still be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.47,0:08:04.75,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,奇跡を起こそうとしないゼロならば
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.03,0:08:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A Zero who can't pull off a miracle\Nwon't gain the support of the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.90,0:08:06.84,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,民衆の支持は得られない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.10,0:08:09.03,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そこまで　お考えでしたか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.63,0:08:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You've thought it that far through, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.17,0:08:12.23,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,しかし　私は現れてほしいと
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.77,0:08:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I {\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}want{\r} him to show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.15,0:08:15.74,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いや　願っているのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.80,0:08:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Or rather, I pray that he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.98,0:08:19.31,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いずこかにおられる　我が姫様のために
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.51,0:08:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,For the sake of Her Highness,\Nwherever she is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.28,0:08:24.00,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なぜ合衆国日本をお認めになったのですか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.81,0:08:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you recognize the U.S.J.?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.31,0:08:27.20,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,朱禁城に確認もせず　独断で
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.31,0:08:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,On your own, without confirmation\Nfrom the Vermilion Forbidden City.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.59,0:08:29.75,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いかに大宦官の1人とはいえ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.28,0:08:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you are one of the High\NEunuchs, that was unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.85,0:08:31.45,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,許されることではありません
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.93,0:08:33.58,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ゼロを利用するにせよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.55,0:08:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what were you planning to use Zero for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.63,0:08:35.05,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いかなる目算があって
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.09,0:08:37.40,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ゼロを利用するなどあってはならぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.52,0:08:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We mustn't use Zero for anything!\NZero must be pleased!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.48,0:08:39.31,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ゼロこそが　幸せ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.41,0:08:40.96,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,天子様の御意向は
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.96,0:08:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And what are the Empress's feelings on this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.05,0:08:42.94,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あんな小娘よりゼロよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.46,0:08:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero is more important than that little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.98,0:08:47.21,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ゼロこそ私を幸せにしてくれるということが絶対の法則
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.57,0:08:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The absolute law I must follow is\Nthat Zero shall bring me happiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.26,0:08:48.73,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,この売国奴が
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.70,0:08:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You damned traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.85,0:08:53.76,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,紅天　すでに死す
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.44,0:08:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The Vermilion Dynasty is dead already.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.90,0:08:57.69,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ダメだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.41,0:09:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}It's no use! Killing him, controlling{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}the information, disguising it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.83,0:09:00.18,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,殺しも　情報操作も　偽装も
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.29,0:09:02.30,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どこをたどっても　ロロがネックになる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.82,0:09:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}No matter what I try,{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Rolo remains an obstacle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.52,0:09:05.55,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,くっ…　処刑が始まる前に　なんとか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.22,0:09:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}I have to find what's behind the information{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}I have before the execution starts!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.84,0:09:07.43,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あの情報の裏付けを…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.82,0:09:17.62,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,かつて　黒の騎士団を名乗り
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.27,0:09:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}It seems that the execution{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}of the rebel terrorists...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.67,0:09:20.55,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,エリア11を混乱させた　テロリストの処刑が
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.37,0:09:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}who formerly called themselves the{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Black Knights will be starting soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.58,0:09:22.68,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,今　正に行われようとしています
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.85,0:09:26.49,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,部下の処刑に果たしてゼロは姿を現すのでしょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.37,0:09:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Will Zero appear to stop the{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}execution of his followers?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.58,0:09:28.05,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ゼロ様　どうか…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.08,0:09:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh Zero, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.09,0:09:28.85,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,藤堂将軍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.34,0:09:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,General Tohdoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.94,0:09:29.86,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,殺さないで
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.38,0:09:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.80,0:09:31.66,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どうして？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.72,0:09:39.60,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ゼロは我々を裏切ったのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.35,0:09:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero betrayed us.\NI doubt he'll come to save us now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.71,0:09:41.63,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,助けに来るはずがない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.65,0:09:44.18,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ぜってぇ～来る　あいつが本物なら
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.06,0:09:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gonna come!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.36,0:09:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's the real one, if he's alive,\Nthen he'll make a miracle happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.35,0:09:47.21,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,生きていたなら　奇跡を起こしにやってくるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:49.14,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,奇跡…か
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.83,0:09:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A miracle, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.36,0:09:50.75,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,警戒を怠るな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.93,0:09:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Maintain tight surveillance!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.84,0:09:52.46,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,可能性は低いが
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.67,0:09:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a long shot, but it's possible C.C. may show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.51,0:09:54.22,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,C.C.の出現はありうる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.99,0:09:59.21,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,扇要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.41,0:10:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Kaname Ohgi... This is the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.59,0:10:01.54,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,これで　終わりになる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.00,0:10:06.23,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,出てこい　ぜろ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.45,0:10:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Show yourself, Zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.39,0:10:09.49,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,義父上　アンドレアス·ダールトンの敵…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.98,0:10:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My father, Andreas Darlton, shall be avenged!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.94,0:10:12.72,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,本隊から　極秘命令です
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.49,0:10:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}I have top secret orders from headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.87,0:10:14.59,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,通信の傍受を避けるため
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.46,0:10:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Communications are being monitored,{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}so I'm to deliver them to you verbally.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.68,0:10:16.83,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,口頭伝達せよとのことですが
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.29,0:10:24.39,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あなたの存在をお借りしますよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.66,0:10:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be filling in for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.85,0:10:30.08,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,これは　どう受け取ったら　いいのかしら
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.37,0:10:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So, just how are we supposed to interpret this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.17,0:10:32.50,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ゼロが現れたら　動いてくれていい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.67,0:10:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If Zero appears, you can act as you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.58,0:10:37.19,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fscx80}我々なら　たとえブリタニアに発砲しても　知らん顔を決め込めると
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.04,0:10:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So, even if we start shooting at the Britannians,\Nyou can pretend you know nothing about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.33,0:10:39.43,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,悪い取引ではないはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.11,0:10:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it's such a bad deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.54,0:10:41.20,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,武官と聞いていたが
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.18,0:10:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You may be a military officer, but\Nyou can play politics as well, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.35,0:10:43.14,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,政治もできるようだな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.61,0:10:47.24,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,キンメル卿　先行量産機に問題はないか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.65,0:10:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Sir Kimmel, any problems with{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}that A.S.E.E.C. mass-pro unit?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.35,0:10:49.08,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,機情が使ったからな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.19,0:10:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}It may have some peculiarities left{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}from when the O.S.I. were using it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.13,0:10:50.75,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,変な癖が残っているかもしれん
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.94,0:10:52.38,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,大事な機体だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.79,0:10:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}It's a valuable machine. Report{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}in if it acts up in any way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.50,0:10:54.82,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,少しでも調子が悪ければ　報告してくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.07,0:10:56.37,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,こちらキンメル
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.93,0:10:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}This is Kimmel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.52,0:10:58.37,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ヴィンセントに異常なし
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.40,0:11:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No problems with Vincent. Moving out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.45,0:10:59.07,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いけます
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.04,0:11:03.98,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ルルーシュ　約束を果たさなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.57,0:11:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Lelouch, if you don't keep your promise, you'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.06,0:11:04.93,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,殺すだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.19,0:11:06.52,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,キルフォード卿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.14,0:11:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Lord Guilford.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.60,0:11:10.14,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,さあ　いよいよ　刑の執行時間です
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.11,0:11:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}It's almost time for the execution!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.23,0:11:13.46,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,黒の騎士団の残党に　正義の裁きが下されます
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.71,0:11:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}The remnants of the Black Knights{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}shall feel the judgment of justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.50,0:11:14.22,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ゼロ様
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.95,0:11:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.41,0:11:15.34,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お願いです
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.98,0:11:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.47,0:11:16.80,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どうか　奇跡を
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.19,0:11:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Make a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.85,0:11:18.14,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,イレヴンたちよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.35,0:11:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Elevens!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.25,0:11:21.96,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お前たちが　信じたゼロは現れなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.86,0:11:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}The Zero which you believed in hasn't shown up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.20,0:11:23.59,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,すべてはまやかし
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.79,0:11:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}It's all been a deception!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.75,0:11:27.82,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ヤツは私の求める正々堂々の勝負から逃げたのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.36,0:11:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He has fled from a fair and honest\Nduel which I requested. Take aim!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.46,0:11:29.62,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,構え
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.88,0:11:35.89,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,嫌だ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.34,0:11:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.03,0:11:36.73,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,みんな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.57,0:11:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.87,0:11:37.50,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,動くな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.37,0:11:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Don't move! If you go out{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}now, you'll just die with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.87,0:11:39.84,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ここから出たら　お前も殺される
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.87,0:11:41.28,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,分かってる　でも…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.34,0:11:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}I know, but!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.34,0:11:42.23,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,もういい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.94,0:11:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Let it end. We've all done a fine job.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.35,0:11:44.46,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,よくやったよ　オレたち
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.97,0:11:45.78,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,違うな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.41,0:11:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.86,0:11:48.64,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,間違ってるぞ　ギルフォード
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.42,0:11:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}You're wrong, Guilford!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.32,0:11:51.07,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,来てくれた　でも…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.85,0:11:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He came! But!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.34,0:11:52.93,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私たちも手が出せない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.99,0:11:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't do anything. What\Ncan he do, all by himself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.28,0:11:55.27,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どうする　たった一人で
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.50,0:11:58.16,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なるほど　後ろに回ったか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.02,0:11:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... You snuck up behind me, Zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.30,0:11:59.31,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ゼロ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.89,0:12:04.03,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ギルフォードよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.43,0:12:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Guilford! Those aren't terrorists you're executing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.17,0:12:07.44,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,貴公が処刑しようとしているのはテロリストではない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.51,0:12:10.57,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,我が合衆国軍　黒の騎士団の兵士だ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.00,0:12:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}They are the Black Knights! Soldiers of{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}the army of the United States of Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.65,0:12:12.25,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,国際法にのっとり
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.11,0:12:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}You expect me to recognize them as{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}prisoners under International Law?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.31,0:12:13.95,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,捕虜として認めよと
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.97,0:12:14.51,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ゼロ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.34,0:12:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.97,0:12:16.97,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,出てきたね　やっぱり
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.54,0:12:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you did come, as I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.18,0:12:20.43,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でも　僕との約束を破ったら　死んでもらうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.91,0:12:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you break your promise\Nto me, I'll kill you, Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.52,0:12:22.62,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ゼロ　いや…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.68,0:12:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Or rather, you, Lelouch Lamperouge!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.90,0:12:24.57,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ルルーシュ·ランペルージ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.69,0:12:36.82,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ゼロです　ゼロが現れました
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.13,0:12:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}It's Zero! Zero has appeared!{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}What a foolish action on his part!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.01,0:12:38.83,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なんという　愚かな行為でしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.88,0:12:39.55,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ゼロが？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.43,0:12:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.68,0:12:40.69,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どうして…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.40,0:12:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.82,0:12:42.28,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,本物なのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.57,0:12:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it the real one?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.37,0:12:44.54,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,決まってんだろ！ゼロ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.77,0:12:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course he is! ZERO-O-O!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.96,0:12:48.90,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そういや　処刑の発表はあったけど　それ以上の報道は…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.74,0:12:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, there was that\Nannouncement of his execution, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.81,0:12:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We've heard nothing more on the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.92,0:12:50.14,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いや　でも…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.34,0:12:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No, but!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.30,0:12:52.06,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs23\an8}一人です　ゼロは一人です
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.65,0:12:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}He's alone! Zero is all alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.14,0:12:56.61,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs23\an8\fscx80}ナイトメア·フレームに乗っているということは　自首が目的ではないのでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.88,0:12:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}As he is riding atop a Knightmare Frame,{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}it's clear that he's not here to surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.69,0:12:59.49,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs23\an8}しかし　一人で戦うつもりなら…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.15,0:12:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}However, if he intends to fight alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.63,0:13:00.42,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ほら　私の言ったとおりでしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.89,0:13:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Just like I said he would!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.47,0:13:04.20,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なら　去年の計画どおりに事を進めましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.16,0:13:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's continue the operation from last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.35,0:13:07.77,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ゼロがこのピンチをくぐり抜けられたらだけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.89,0:13:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Assuming Zero can wriggle out\Nof this little pinch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.68,0:13:10.61,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,咲世子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.27,0:13:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayoko, I'd like you to make\Npreparations for that contingency plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.66,0:13:13.91,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,先々のために　例の手配準備に入ってほしい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.95,0:13:16.57,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs23\an8}ブリタニア軍側は…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.27,0:13:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}The Britannian soldiers seem{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}to be waiting for Zero's move.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.28,0:13:17.29,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ルルーシュ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.77,0:13:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Lelouch?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.34,0:13:18.75,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ロロが付いています
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.94,0:13:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Rolo's with him. They've been at the\NSpiral Theater for the last 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.89,0:13:21.05,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,30分前からスパイラルシアターに
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.67,0:13:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}We've yet to see a major move. The tense{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}atmosphere at the execution site continues to flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.89,0:13:25.78,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お久しぶりです　ギルフォード卿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.31,0:13:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}It's been quite a while, Lord Guilford.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.89,0:13:28.27,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,出てきて　昔話でもいかがですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.58,0:13:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Why don't you come out and we{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}can talk about the good old days?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.33,0:13:31.19,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,せっかくのお誘いだが　遠慮しておこう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.92,0:13:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Tempting as that invitation is,{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}I'll stay where I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.27,0:13:34.91,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,過去の因縁にはナイトメアでお応えしたいが
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.79,0:13:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Why don't we settle our past{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}grudges inside our Knightmares?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.07,0:13:37.86,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,外に出てこないんじゃギアスが使えない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.72,0:13:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless Guilford comes out,\Nhe can't use his Geass!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.99,0:13:39.84,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ふん　君らしいな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.56,0:13:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Hmpf! How typical of you!{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Then let's set some rules!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.01,0:13:41.50,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,では　ルールを決めよう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.64,0:13:42.51,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ルール？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.36,0:13:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Rules?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.72,0:13:44.39,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,決闘のルールだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.40,0:13:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}The rules of our duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.21,0:13:48.03,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,決着は1対1で　つけるべきだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.63,0:13:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll settle this one-on-one!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.09,0:13:51.04,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いいだろう　ほかの者には　手を出させない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.64,0:13:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. No one else will interfere with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.22,0:13:52.60,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,武器は1つだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.84,0:13:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}We will each have only one weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.67,0:13:53.45,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,よかろう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.24,0:13:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Agreed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.19,0:13:58.51,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私の武器はこれだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.35,0:13:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}I choose this as my weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.81,0:14:01.72,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,では　私はその盾を貸してもらおう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:14:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Then I shall borrow that shield as mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.87,0:14:03.26,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何？それは…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.35,0:14:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}What? But, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.45,0:14:04.44,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,これでいい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.92,0:14:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}It will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.72,0:14:06.70,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,暴徒鎮圧用のシールドじゃあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.15,0:14:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,A riot shield?\NDid he plan from the start...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.07,0:14:08.88,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,まさか　最初っから…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.01,0:14:10.32,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,自決する気か
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.49,0:14:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...to kill himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.96,0:14:14.58,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,失望だな　ゼロ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.43,0:14:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You disappoint me, Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.97,0:14:16.07,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どうしますか？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.63,0:14:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What shall we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:20.98,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,寄生虫たる大宦官　その一人を始末できた借りがある
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.80,0:14:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I owe him a debt for giving me a way to\Ndeal with that parasite of a high eunuch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.01,0:14:24.73,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,しかし　これは永続調和に基づく契りではない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,However, this isn't a pledge\Nbased on Permanent Harmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.97,0:14:30.04,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ゼロが無能ならば\N黒の騎士団は外交の道具となってもらうしかないだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.47,0:14:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If Zero turns out to be incompetent, then we'll just\Nuse the Black Knights as our diplomatic tools.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.74,0:14:33.75,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,質問しよう　ギルフォード卿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.21,0:14:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question for you, Lord Guilford.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.92,0:14:37.80,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,正義で倒せない悪がいるとき　君はどうする？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.62,0:14:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}What do you do when there is an{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}evil you cannot defeat by justice?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.97,0:14:41.53,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,悪に手を染めてでも　悪を倒すか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.45,0:14:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Do you stain your hands with{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}evil so as to destroy evil?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.58,0:14:46.22,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それとも己が正義を貫き悪に屈するをよしとするか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.12,0:14:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Or do you uphold your justice{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}even if you must surrender to evil?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.28,0:14:48.26,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いずれにせよ　悪は残る
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.70,0:14:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,In either case, evil remains.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.45,0:14:50.89,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,矛盾　言葉遊びか…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.00,0:14:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,A contradiction... Is it a word play?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.03,0:14:53.92,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,我が正義は　姫様の下に
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.67,0:14:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Justice is whatever my princess says it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.49,0:14:59.38,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なるほど　私なら　悪をなして　巨悪を討つ!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.10,0:14:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! In my case...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.37,0:15:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}I commit evil in order to destroy the greater evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.60,0:15:01.42,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,イエス　ユア　ハイネス
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.01,0:15:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.34,0:15:06.01,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,これは！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.81,0:15:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What the?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.86,0:15:10.96,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,じ…地震！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.25,0:15:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,E- Earthquake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.12,0:15:12.93,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いや　この作戦は…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.65,0:15:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No! This strategy is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.18,0:15:15.08,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ブラックリベリオンのときの！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.96,0:15:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The one from the Black Rebellion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.55,0:15:25.43,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,第12歩兵部隊　レベル4の階層コントロールルームに向かえ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.00,0:15:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Infantry unit 12!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.60,0:15:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Head for the control room on level 4!{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}One of Zero's men is in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.75,0:15:26.74,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ゼロの部下が…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.03,0:15:30.02,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,カレン突入指揮を執れ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.50,0:15:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Kallen! Charge in and take command!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.05,0:15:30.55,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.47,0:15:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger! Autonomous armored\Ncombat machine unit, follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.77,0:15:32.89,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,自在戦闘装甲機部隊はついてこい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.94,0:15:35.66,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,扇さんたちの救出が　最優先だ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.58,0:15:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Saving Ohgi and the others has top priority!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.49,0:15:38.61,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,アルファ4より　アルファ1　応答願います
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.85,0:15:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Alpha 4 to alpha 1! Please respond!\NAlpha 1! Alpha 1! Shit! Somebody, answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.64,0:15:39.77,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,アルファ1　アルファ1！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.03,0:15:41.07,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,くそ　誰か…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.89,0:15:44.52,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ひきょうな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.12,0:15:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You dishonorable!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.19,0:15:49.75,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何が1対1か
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.69,0:15:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,One-on-one my ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.38,0:15:53.98,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,な　何っ！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.60,0:15:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.06,0:15:56.87,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,バート
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.57,0:15:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Bart!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.95,0:16:02.29,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,黒の騎士団よ　敵は我が領内に落ちた
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.50,0:16:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Black Knights!\NThe enemies have fallen into our territory!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.37,0:16:05.58,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ブリタニア軍を壊滅し同胞を救い出せ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.94,0:16:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Wipe out the Britannian forces{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}and save your comrades!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.65,0:16:06.52,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,同胞…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.11,0:16:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Comrades...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.47,0:16:10.29,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,租界の構造を逆手に取ったか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.91,0:16:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He used the structure of the\Nsettlement against them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.30,0:16:14.19,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,急げ　ブリタニアが体勢を整える前に全員解放するんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.61,0:16:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up! Release everyone before\Nthe Britannian forces can regroup!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.21,0:16:17.39,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,逃げられてしまう　中華連邦内に…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.78,0:16:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They're going to escape!\NRight into the Chinese Federation!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.52,0:16:20.35,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,我々の目的はあくまでC.C.だ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.32,0:16:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,C.C. remains our primary target!\NLeave this to Guilford!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.42,0:16:22.61,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そちらは　ギルフォードに任せておけ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.07,0:16:24.35,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,テロリストが
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.66,0:16:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Damned terrorists!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.89,0:16:31.63,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ブリタニア　ここはね　もう日本の領土なんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.16,0:16:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Britannia!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.46,0:16:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Japanese territory now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.84,0:16:33.62,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,日本など　存在しない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.40,0:16:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Japan doesn't exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:34.46,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あっそ…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.14,0:16:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?\NThis is why I hate Britannia!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.93,0:16:36.46,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,これだから　ブリタニアは…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.01,0:16:41.24,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,さらばだ　イレヴンのエース
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.37,0:16:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Eleven ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.49,0:16:47.30,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,防いだ…この距離で
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.01,0:16:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Blocked! At this range?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.46,0:16:53.08,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fscx90}これが輻射波動　懐に入ったときに　私の勝ちは決まっていたの
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.95,0:16:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}This is the radiant wave surger!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.62,0:16:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}The moment you came in close,{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}my victory was assured!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.95,0:16:54.93,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,じゃあね
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.46,0:16:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So long.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.42,0:17:03.83,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,よくも　アルフレッドを…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.76,0:17:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Alfred! How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.92,0:17:06.88,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,撃つな　ここは中華連邦の治外法権区だぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.30,0:17:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Don't shoot!{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}This is Chinese Federation territory!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.94,0:17:07.70,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,しかし…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.50,0:17:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.81,0:17:09.40,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,報道カメラも入ってるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.30,0:17:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}There are broadcast cameras here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.50,0:17:11.90,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ヴィ…ヴィンセントが
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.01,0:17:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Th- The Vincent!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.37,0:17:14.21,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ヴィンセントが突入しました
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.84,0:17:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}The Vincent's charged inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.45,0:17:28.45,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,こっちは動けない　逃げて
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.09,0:17:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't move from here!\NRun for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.29,0:17:31.16,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,来たか…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.79,0:17:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}You've come...{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}You've finally come, Rolo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.37,0:17:33.43,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,来てしまったのか？ロロ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.90,0:17:38.51,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,やっぱり逃げるんですね？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.40,0:17:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}So, you are running.{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}So much for your promise to give me C.C....
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.76,0:17:40.73,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,C.C.を差し出す約束は？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.14,0:17:43.92,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ルルーシュ　最初から僕にうそを…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.60,0:17:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Lelouch...{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}You were lying to me from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.38,0:17:48.64,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,まだ…　まだ捕まるわけには…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.81,0:17:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Not yet!{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}I can't be caught yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.81,0:17:51.03,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,僕に未来をくれると言ったくせに…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.44,0:17:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}All that talk about{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}giving me a future!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.31,0:17:52.85,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ここで　死ぬわけには…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.81,0:17:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}I can't die here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.16,0:17:56.47,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,任務さえ果たせば　未来はつながるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.18,0:17:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}If I just complete my mission,{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}I'll open the way to my future!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.80,0:18:02.58,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,しまった…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.19,0:18:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.74,0:18:05.31,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,物理現象は止められない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.13,0:18:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}I can't stop a physical object!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.39,0:18:10.01,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,直撃コースだ　こんな所で…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.80,0:18:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}It'll be a direct hit!{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}There's no way I can dodge it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.66,0:18:16.63,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,やめろ　デヴィッド
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.97,0:18:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}David, stop! If you hit the Chinese{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Federation consulate, it'll be an act of war!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.81,0:18:19.73,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,総領事館にあたったら　中華連邦との戦争になるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.88,0:18:20.69,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,分かってる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.34,0:18:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.95,0:18:23.47,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,な…なぜ…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.58,0:18:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.34,0:18:28.95,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どうして　僕を…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.28,0:18:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.19,0:18:31.38,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お前が　弟だから…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.48,0:18:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Because... you're my little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.61,0:18:37.84,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fscx70}植え付けられた記憶だったとしても　お前と過ごしたあの時間に　うそはなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.09,0:18:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}The memories may have been planted in me,{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}but the time we spent together was real!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.48,0:18:42.75,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,今までのことが　うそじゃなかったって…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.03,0:18:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You're saying...\NAll the things we did till now weren't a lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.28,0:18:44.87,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お前が弟だから…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.67,0:18:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're my little brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.80,0:18:49.12,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,弟？僕が…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.23,0:18:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.70,0:18:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.37,0:18:55.11,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あの日　誕生日がなかった僕に　初めて…それも？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.81,0:18:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That day... After never having a\Nbirthday ever, for the first time, I!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.64,0:18:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that's why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.64,0:18:58.90,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,自分の命が大事だってそう言ったくせに
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.08,0:18:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What about when you said\Nyour life was more important?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.39,0:19:01.11,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そんな　くだらない理由で…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.85,0:19:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}For such a stupid reason, you'd?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.37,0:19:05.32,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,約束したからな　お前の新しい未来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.72,0:19:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}I made a promise to you.{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}For your new future.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.36,0:19:08.95,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お前の未来は　オレと…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.89,0:19:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Your future... with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.33,0:19:12.57,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ゼロ　ここで因縁を断とう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.86,0:19:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Zero! We'll settle things now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.73,0:19:14.20,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私の一撃で
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.23,0:19:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,With one blow from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.22,0:19:17.54,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,この鉄槌で
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.77,0:19:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,With this iron hammer!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.46,0:19:25.12,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.01,0:19:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}What?! Sir Kimmel,{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}what's the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.33,0:19:26.77,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どういうつもりか？キンメル卿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.26,0:19:28.23,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あっ　いや　これは…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.28,0:19:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, no! I just!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.31,0:19:30.58,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,まさか　ゼロの仲間か！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.01,0:19:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you one of Zero's men?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.63,0:19:33.98,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ちがう…僕は　ルルーシュが死ぬと　任務が…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.08,0:19:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I... If Lelouch dies,\Nthen my mission is!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.06,0:19:34.99,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いや　でも…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.38,0:19:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No, but...\NWhat am I doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.17,0:19:36.80,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何をしているんだ　僕は
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.71,0:19:42.27,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.02,0:19:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.42,0:19:44.47,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ロロ　まずい　ヴィレッタ先生からだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.92,0:19:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Rolo? Trouble. It's Coach Villetta.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.15,0:19:46.55,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,IMオープンでつなぐぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.15,0:19:46.55,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs23}（IM ：Instant Messenger）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.59,0:19:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}I'll connect you on the open I.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.97,0:19:49.16,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ロロか？どこに行っていた？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.40,0:19:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Rolo? Where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.43,0:19:50.47,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,その…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.20,0:19:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.70,0:19:51.89,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,やだな　先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.20,0:19:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Coach, c'mon!\NCan't we even go to the toilet in peace?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.06,0:19:54.57,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,トイレぐらい別々にさせてくださいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.71,0:19:57.36,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,で　なんでしたっけ？さっきの…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.57,0:19:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}So, what were you calling about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.48,0:19:59.40,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,総領事館の話だろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.97,0:19:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,About the consulate, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.46,0:20:01.97,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ああ～　すごい騒ぎらしいですね
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.91,0:20:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Oh, yeah. Looks like a real mess down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.06,0:20:05.04,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いけない　今までのことが知られたら…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.71,0:20:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Uh-oh! If they find out what's happened,{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}I'll be thrown out of the O.S. I!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.07,0:20:06.43,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,機情から排除される
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.73,0:20:07.76,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あの人だって…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.25,0:20:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Even that person would!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.59,0:20:09.77,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,分かっていますよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.05,0:20:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}I understand. I'll keep my little{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}brother out of danger from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.16,0:20:12.83,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,もう　危ないことに　弟を巻き込みません
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.37,0:20:15.32,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,当たり前じゃないですか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.09,0:20:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not! People being killed is\Nno world for Rolo to be involved in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.41,0:20:18.20,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ロロには　人殺しがある世界なんて似合わない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.58,0:20:22.78,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そこまでだ　ブリタニアの諸君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.10,0:20:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough, Britannians!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.23,0:20:25.72,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,これ以上は武力介入とみなす
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.23,0:20:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Any further action will be taken as{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}armed intervention. Withdraw at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.87,0:20:26.96,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,引き揚げたまえ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.81,0:20:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,HEY!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.11,0:20:34.20,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,よかったぁ…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.61,0:20:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.77,0:20:35.47,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,扇さん
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.21,0:20:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohgi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.52,0:20:36.21,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,扇…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.26,0:20:37.78,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ありがとう　カレン
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.75,0:20:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Kallen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.02,0:20:41.65,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ううん　藤堂さんたちも…よかった
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.38,0:20:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-uh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.85,0:20:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And Tohdoh and the others...\NThank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.75,0:20:43.87,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,すまない　迷惑を掛けた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.28,0:20:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for being such trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.09,0:20:45.54,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,苦労したんでしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.65,0:20:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Must have been hard for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.47,0:20:47.48,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そっちだって…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.96,0:20:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.62,0:20:49.45,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なあ　あのナイトメアは？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.12,0:20:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, who's in that Knightmare?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.48,0:20:51.27,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,さあ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.09,0:20:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I dunno. It was an enemy unit, but\NI don't know who's piloting it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.51,0:20:53.64,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あの機体は　敵だったんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.72,0:20:55.38,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,今のパイロットは　私も…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.99,0:20:57.71,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ゼロを守ったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.60,0:21:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,They protected Zero. At the very\Nleast, they're not an enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.83,0:21:00.06,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,少なくとも　敵ではないだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.66,0:21:03.95,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,C.C.がいるのに　僕は　もう…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.10,0:21:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,C.C.'s right here, but now I!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.34,0:21:07.96,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,最初から　ブリタニアには　安らぎはなかったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.77,0:21:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}From the beginning,{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}you never felt at ease with Britannia.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.28,0:21:10.45,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お前の居場所は　ここにある
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.78,0:21:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Here is where you belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.52,0:21:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Heh... Now he's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.78,0:21:14.85,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ふ　落ちたな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.37,0:21:18.19,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,こんな資料を司令室に残しているぐらいだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.92,0:21:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Convenient, his leaving this{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}data in the control room.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.39,0:21:20.67,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ギアスしか取り柄がないのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.99,0:21:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}I think the only value{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}he has is for his Geass.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.06,0:21:23.49,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,こいつのパスワードが役に立つとはな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.52,0:21:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}The password in this came in handy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.64,0:21:24.48,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それに…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.16,0:21:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}As well as...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.39,0:21:26.94,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,パターン　デルタ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.99,0:21:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Pattern Delta.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.04,0:21:27.83,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.26,0:21:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct. When Zero's unit takes that course,\Nshoot the pursuing Knightmare from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.96,0:21:32.54,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ゼロの機体がその軌道を取ったとき\N追っているナイトメアを背後から撃て
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.56,0:21:37.37,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fscx80}その後　ゼロが脱出したなら　相手のナイトメアを完全に破壊しろ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.33,0:21:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, if Zero escapes,\Ndestroy the opposing Knightmare completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.57,0:21:40.63,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,脱出しない場合は　その場で待機
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.11,0:21:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If he does not escape,\Nstand by where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.70,0:21:42.67,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ああ…よく分かった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.18,0:21:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. I understand perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.89,0:21:49.65,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ナナリーがいるべき所を　奪い取った偽者め
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.45,0:21:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}You damned little phony,{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}trying to take Nunnally's place!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.77,0:21:54.38,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,さんざん　使い倒して　ボロぞうきんのように　捨ててやる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.42,0:21:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}I'll use you up and then throw you{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}away like a ragged dust cloth!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.12,0:22:07.91,edj-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\fad(100,100)\an8}胸の中 いつか拾った
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.80,0:22:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Mune no naka itsuka hirotta\NSomeday let's try to pick up and rebuild
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.92,0:22:13.86,edj-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\fad(100,100)\an8}幸せの欠片 集めてみよう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.77,0:22:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiawase no kakera atsumete miyou\NThe fragments of happiness in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.48,0:22:19.13,edj-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\fad(100,100)\an8}忘れかけていたメロディー
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.35,0:22:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasurekaketeita melody\NThat nearly forgotten melody
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.57,0:22:27.58,edj-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\fad(100,600)\an8}色褪せず僕の真ん中に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.48,0:22:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Iroasezu boku no man'naka ni\NStay vivid, deep inside of me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.73,0:22:39.39,edj-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\fad(100,100)\an8}ありがとう 心から 僕に今があるのはみんなのおかげさ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.66,0:22:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Arigatou kokoro kara\NI thank you from the bottom of my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.43,0:22:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Boku ni ima ga aru no wa minna no okagesa\NEverything I have now, I owe to everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.83,0:22:50.01,edj-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\fad(100,100)\an8}ありがとう 心から 次は僕がみんなにハッピー贈るよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.64,0:22:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Arigatou kokoro kara\NI thank you from the bottom of my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.41,0:22:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsugi wa boku ga minna ni happy okuru yo\NNext I'll send happiness to everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.98,0:23:02.06,edj-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\fad(100,100)\an8}何もかも忘れないよ あの日の僕も僕だから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.78,0:22:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanimokamo wasurenai yo\NI won't forget anything
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.89,0:23:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ano hi no boku mo boku dakara\NBecause I'm still the same as I was that day
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.51,0:23:11.77,edj-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\fad(100,100)\an8}「大好きだよ」って　いつも言ってあげなきゃ駄目だね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.33,0:23:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Daisuki da yo'tte itsumo\NYou need me to keep on saying
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.47,0:23:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Itte agenakya dame da ne\NHow much I love you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.79,0:23:22.15,edj-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\fad(100,100)\an8}涙がこぼれそうな長い夜は ふっと振り返って
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.54,0:23:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Namida ga kobore sou na nagai yoru wa\NOn those long nights, your tears about to overflow
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.24,0:23:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Futto furikaette\NJust turn around
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.70,0:23:35.17,edj-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\fad(100,100)\an8}足跡を辿るんだ あの日を忘れないように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.61,0:23:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ashiato wo tadorun'da\NFollow those footprints
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.65,0:23:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ano hi wo wasurenai you ni\NSo that you'll never forget that day
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.14,0:23:38.74,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何が　ロロ·ランペルージだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.94,0:23:41.12,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あんなヤツを弟と思っていたなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.06,0:23:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Who does Rolo Lamperouge think he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.76,0:23:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thinking he was my little brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.19,0:23:42.88,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,身震いするほどの屈辱だ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.70,0:23:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I practically shudder from the disgrace!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.05,0:23:46.38,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,しかし　お前が便利な駒になるのなら…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.73,0:23:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a shame, but if he'd remained\Nloyal to his duty to the O.S.I.,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.55,0:23:47.79,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,だが　忘れるな
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.98,0:23:50.40,zhengwen-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お前は　ナナリーの偽者でしか…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.24,0:23:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,he would have been killed right\Nthen and there and I'd be rid of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.71,0:23:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, you'll make a convenient pawn,\Nso I'll let you remain at my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.08,0:23:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, never forget!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.68,0:24:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,All you are is a fake Nunnally!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.01,0:24:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the day I can use you\Nbest on the chessboard comes,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.48,0:24:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll keep playing this game of\Nbeing your brother for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.94,0:24:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,KNIGHTS OF THE ROUND
